{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a2d8ffb03c","title":"要求档案公开的理由","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"23414af509","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":11,"articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1534c238a5","name":"紫外线"},{"id":"345d937900","name":"争鸣委员会"},{"id":"4c0546f58a","name":"成都工学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f31c5ef49e","type":"title","text":"要求档案公开的理由","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"id":"046b963dc0","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院争鸣委员会紫外线","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"id":"e0f3d92d16","type":"paragraph","text":"1．解放前的档案成为统治善良人民的工具，现在解放了，人民掌握了政权，档案既然是个人历史的记载，为什么还对个人保密，为什么不能公开，我们坚决呼吁要求个人命运自己主宰。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"id":"ea3791dce1","type":"paragraph","text":"2．档案不公开，成为官僚主义发展的温床，使那些抱有不纯企图的政客们，有可能私设法庭，实行私人报复，使人事处驾临于一切组织之上，作威作福，大笔挥乱加评语任意宰割我们的命运。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"id":"b79be82284","type":"appellation","text":"3．档案不公开真理不抬头，青年的积极性不能发挥，青年人不敢向错误的领导斗争。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"id":"2ac5f6fb49","type":"paragraph","text":"4．档案公开，自己知道其优缺点，也好加速自己的进步。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"id":"4fa957fb8d","type":"paragraph","text":"化机54争鸣委员会","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"id":"c8481bb09c","type":"paragraph","text":" 紫外线第二期","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"id":"7cbbc96740","type":"subtitle","text":"一、反对班三角：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"id":"ea87922a18","type":"paragraph","text":"班三角不等边，一边长来两边宽，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a2d8ffb03c"},{"i